<%# ÈÄöÂ∏∏„ÅÆ„Éï„É©„ÉÉ„Ç∑„É•„É°„ÉÉ„Çª„Éº„Ç∏Âá¶ÁêÜ %>
<% flash.each do |message_type, message| %>
<% 
  # „Éà„É≠„Éï„Ç£„Éº„ÅØÁâπÂà•„Å™Âá¶ÁêÜ„Çí„Åô„Çã„Åü„ÇÅ„Çπ„Ç≠„ÉÉ„Éó
  next if message_type == 'trophy' 

  # Bootstrap„ÅÆdanger„Çø„Ç§„Éó„ÇídaisyUI„ÅÆerror„Å´Â§âÊèõ
  alert_class = message_type
  if message_type == 'danger'
    alert_class = 'error'
  end
%>
<div role="alert" class="alert alert-<%= alert_class %> mb-4">
    <% if alert_class == 'error' %>
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
            d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
    </svg>
    <% elsif alert_class == 'success' %>
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
    </svg>
    <% elsif alert_class == 'info' %>
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
            d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
    </svg>
    <% elsif alert_class == 'warning' %>
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
            d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
    </svg>
    <% end %>
    <span><%= message %></span>
</div>
<% end %>

